list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1665449874.3978834", "card_id": "Q_24892260", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 186}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么足球类游戏都是 5 到 30 分钟，而没有完整 90 分钟的比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如果说是因为玩一盘 90 分钟的比赛会感到枯燥，那为什么看一场 90 分钟的足球比赛不会感到枯燥呢？（对球迷 + 足球游戏迷来说）。难道亲身参与比赛不是比观看一场比赛更有乐趣吗？ 周南：足球游戏为什么会在短短几分钟内打入那么多进球，它和正常足球比赛的不同在哪里？ 现在足球游戏就是个十五分钟一盘的快餐游戏，十五分钟的设计节奏必然加快。真要让玩家踢满九十分钟还要估计每个球员的不确定性，传球的时候还随机无法判定落点，前场传着球突然后场两球员打起来了，那也太硬核、太血狮了，恐怕只有极少数的玩家才能承受得住这种精神压力而不摔手柄。 刘小慧补充：在 EA 的 FIFA2002 的时代，游戏中设置的比赛时间是有 90 分钟的，当时我就试过一次 90 分钟，踢了电脑 105：0，所以该问题不成立；但现在的足球游戏基本都已取消了这个选项，所以原题目虽不成立，但有实际意义。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/731a8ca295a20ee75de58c6366defbd5_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/24892260"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Iq8OPgM7H+c9CEAMaBzIxMzg5MTcg4evFnwUwGjjKBEAacggyNDg5MjI2MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1665449874.3989847", "card_id": "Q_550967142", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "继瑜伽裤后，运动内衣穿搭成为新的流行风向标，这股风潮到底是怎么刮起来的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-37ccd522b985d797afd6c35580b4dc58_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "44 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/550967142"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq8OPgM7H+c9CEAMaCDg0NzIwOTk3IMiqu5gGMBc49AJAG3IJNTUwOTY3MTQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1665449874.399648", "card_id": "Q_558476073", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男子年薪相比招聘时承诺年薪少发 7 万，被判公司补足，如何从法律角度解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2020 年初，南京的蔡先生与一家公司签订劳动合同，对方承诺年收入在 16-18 万元。蔡先生慎重考虑后，于当年 3 月入职。然而，蔡先生在年底时发现年收入只有 9 万多元，辞职后进行劳动仲裁无果，将原公司告上法庭。原公司表示，当时与蔡先生的合同约定月工资为 3000 元，招聘主管承诺的年薪并不能代表公司。法院审理认为，招聘人员履行职务行为，做出的承诺对公司具有约束力，且双方在微信中对工资有过明确表示，可作为证据。因此，法院判决原公司补足工资差额 69500 元，公司不服提起上诉，二审被法院驳回上诉请求。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c372a1bc9a99689367b8b4eb731fc0dc_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/558476073"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq8OPgM7H+c9CEAMaCDg2Mzg4NTE3IK2DjpoGMAQ4mQFAHHIJNTU4NDc2MDczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1665449874.4005222", "card_id": "Q_445788452", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 211}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么铃木园子没有喜欢上工藤新一?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4e64b467f5d93e8cd24583c1d637c5d7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445788452"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq8OPgM7H+c9CEAMaCDYxMzQyNzMyIIqfzoEGMAY45wJAHXIJNDQ1Nzg4NDUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1665449874.4011168", "card_id": "Q_558273173", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中学没接触过编程，大学能学名校的计算机吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-97d0e1e09dfa2dcaff33bf22e25c9263_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/558273173"}}, "attache